text: Nic Stene (25 May 1921 - 20 May 2006) was a Norwegian speed skater, born in Trondheim. He competed at the 1952 Winter Olympics in Oslo, where he placed 15th in the 1,500 m. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1921 births Category:2006 deaths Category:Norwegian male speed skaters Category:Olympic speed skaters of Norway Category:Speed skaters at the 1952 Winter Olympics
